Th%C3%A1i-Th%C3%A2n/author-FbbINXH7lzqgF9ytJv8P4Q">Thái Thân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%89nh-%C4%91%E1%BB%83-d%E1%BA%ABn-ng%C3%A2n-b%C3%ACnh/poem-fEvivJabPd3uwuqTNX3otg">Tỉnh để dẫn ngân bình - 井底引銀瓶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-H%E1%BB%8Dc-Thu%E1%BA%A7n/T%E1%BB%91ng-nh%C3%A2n-quy-Giang-T%C3%A2y/poem-uSEhrRUiHApgv1ERs4czLA">Tống nhân quy Giang Tây - 送人歸江西</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-H%E1%BB%8Dc-Thu%E1%BA%A7n/author-cD-xARmvY4kC1RxUWEbBZg">Trịnh Học Thuần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%ABu-Vi%E1%BB%85n/%E1%BB%B6-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-HLgiIFMcm7ihnvlD3EqKlQ">Ỷ nguyệt - 倚月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%ABu-Vi%E1%BB%85n/author-sRemHKkmYCdxkkHc58hcHA">Cừu Viễn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
